1. Create a View for employee table to get the salary if it is <10000 mark it as 'LOW' otherwise 'MODERATE' in separate column 'Sal_Status'.
  So the result of view should display the following details like EmpID,EmpName,Department,Salary,Sal_Status.

create view emp_salary_status as
select 
emp_id as EmpID,
emp_name as EmpName,
department as Department,
salary as Salary,
if(salary < 10000, 'LOW', 'MODERATE') as Sal_Status
from employee;

